    home += card('Proof Card 002','Sovereign Procurement Trust Room. A procurement team receives a public-safe evidence room.','gold')
    home += card('Proof Card 003','Sovereign AI Procurement Control Tower. A buyer governance question becomes a proof mission, Evidence Docket, credential, reputation update, and reusable RSI artifact.','dark')
    home += '</div></section><section class="section"><h2>Why it creates demand</h2><div class="grid2">'
    home += card('For buyers','It answers the question: can this AI workflow system be trusted, audited, rolled back, and improved safely?')
    home += card('For sponsors','It turns abstract AI interest into specific proof missions with evidence, reviewer validation, and public-safe Proof Cards.')
    home += card('For builders','It creates a clear route from useful work to proof, credential, reputation, and better missions.')
    home += card('For the institution','It makes recursive self-improvement practical: only artifacts that survive proof can improve future work.')
    home += '</div><div class="footercta"><a class="btn" href="flagship-use-case.html">Open the flagship use case</a><a class="btn alt" href="agialpha-ledger-route.html">See the AGIALPHA route</a></div></section>'
    write_page(out,'index.html','GoalOS AGIALPHA Ascension Demand Center',home,'index.html')
    flagship = hero('Proof Card 003','Sovereign AI Procurement Control Tower','A sovereign or enterprise buyer asks whether an AI workflow system can be trusted. GoalOS turns that question into a proof mission. AGIALPHA coordinates the proof work. The Evidence Docket makes the answer auditable.',chips)
    flagship += '<section class="section"><h2>The executive problem</h2><p class="intro">AI adoption is blocked less by model output than by trust: procurement, auditability, governance, rollback, evidence, and accountability. This use case turns that blocker into a proof-generating machine.</p><div class="quote">GoalOS turns buyer trust into proof. AGIALPHA coordinates the mission. Reviewers validate the evidence. Only proven artifacts earn upgrade rights.</div><div class="grid">'
    flagship += card('Before','A buyer receives a polished AI promise but cannot verify workflow safety, rollback, evidence, review quality, or improvement discipline.')
