    ledger = hero('AGIALPHA route','Where AGIALPHA becomes useful','AGIALPHA is not required for a normal buyer to read the site. It becomes useful when sponsors, builders, reviewers, proof cards, credentials, reputation, and settlement need shared coordination.')
